name: Ruralité — 02
description:
For the last-plus 6 years, I have been slowly walking through Indre and Creuse departments (France) in order to offer places the possibility of appearing for who they are: a territorial significance. A testimony of it. Hamlets, villages, small urban centers, crossroads, gas stations, shops ... generic elements, places and landscapes of little. Out of scope, but with an atmosphere which gives them a status of quasi-character with a feeling of abandonment.
